            times the branching fraction relative to that of the \(B_{c}^{+} \to J/\psi D_{s}^{+}\) decay at centre-of-mass energies 
            of \(8\) and \(13~\rm{TeV}\), in the \(\Xi_{bc}^{+}\) and in the \(B_{c}^{+}\) rapidity and transverse-momentum ranges 
            from \(2.0\) to \(4.5\) and \(0\) to \(20~\rm{GeV}/c\), respectively. Upper limits are presented as a function of the 
            \(\Xi_{bc}^{+}\) mass and lifetime.},
